msgstr "Fakultattiv"

msgctxt "#31390"
msgid "Skin default"
msgstr "Inadempjenza tal-ġilda"

msgctxt "#31400"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE INTERFACE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Change the skin · Set language and region · Setup remote controls[CR]Set up a screensaver · Setup master lock"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURA IS-SETTINGS TAL-INTERFACE[/B][CR][CR]Ibdel il-ġilda · Issettja l-lingwa u r-reġjun · Issettja l-kontrolli mill-bogħod[CR]Twaqqaf screensaver · Issettja l-master lock"

msgctxt "#31401"
msgid "Menu - press 'OK'"
msgstr "Menu - agħfas 'OK'"

msgctxt "#31402"
msgid "Enable startup video intro"
msgstr "Ippermetti l-introduzzjoni tal-vidjo tal-istartjar"

msgctxt "#31405"
msgid "[B]MONITOR YOUR SYSTEM[/B][CR][CR]Check out your hardware · Monitor CPU usage[CR]Check Kodi revision number"
msgstr "[B]IMMONIORA S-SISTEMA TIEGĦEK[/B][CR][CR]Iċċekkja l-ħardwer tiegħek · Immonitorja l-użu tas-CPU[CR]Iċċekkja n-numru tar-reviżjoni Kodi"

msgctxt "#31406"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SYSTEM SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup and calibrate displays · Configure audio output · [CR]Set power saving options · Enable debugging"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURA IS-SETTINGS TAS-SISTEMA[/B][CR][CR]Issettja u tikkalibra l-wirjiet · Ikkonfigura l-output tal-awdjo · [CR]Issettja l-għażliet għall-iffrankar tal-enerġija · Ippermetti d-debugging"

msgctxt "#31407"
msgid "[B]SETUP PROFILES[/B][CR][CR]Setup and manage user profiles · Enable login screen[CR]Change password · Add a profile picture"
msgstr "[B]SETUP PROFILES[/B][CR][CR]Imwaqqaf u mmaniġġja l-profili tal-utent · Ippermetti l-iskrin tal-login[CR]Ibdel il-password · Żid stampa tal-profil"

msgctxt "#31409"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE TV SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Change full screen info · Manage EPG data settings"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURA SETTINGS tat-TV[/B][CR][CR]Ibdel l-informazzjoni tal-iskrin sħiħ · Immaniġġja s-settings tad-dejta tal-EPG"

msgctxt "#31410"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SERVICE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup control of Kodi via UPnP and HTTP · Configure file sharing[CR]Enable Zeroconf · Configure AirPlay"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURA IS-SETTINGS TA' SERVIZZ[/B][CR][CR]Imwaqqaf il-kontroll ta' Kodi permezz ta' UPnP u HTTP · Ikkonfigura l-qsim tal-fajls[CR]Ippermetti Zeroconf · Ikkonfigura AirPlay"

msgctxt "#31412"
msgid "Select section"
msgstr "Agħżel it-taqsima"

msgctxt "#31413"
msgid "Local subtitle available"
msgstr "Sottotitolu lokali disponibbli"

msgctxt "#31414"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE PLAYER SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Configure video playback · Configure music playback · Configure picture slideshow[CR]Configure video language and subtitles"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURA IS-SETTINGS TAL-PLAYER[/B][CR][CR]Kkonfigura l-daqq tal-vidjo · Ikkonfigura l-plejbek tal-mużika · Ikkonfigura l-wiri tal-istampa[CR]Ikkonfigura l-lingwa u s-sottotitli tal-vidjo"

msgctxt "#31415"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE MEDIA SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Set default select action · Configure file list options · Configure metadata options[CR]Manage databases"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURA IS-SETTINGS TAL-MEDJA[/B][CR][CR]Issettja l-azzjoni tal-għażla default · Ikkonfigura l-għażliet tal-lista tal-fajls · Ikkonfigura l-għażliet tal-metadata[CR]Immaniġġja l-bażijiet tad-data"

msgctxt "#31421"
msgid "Select your Kodi user profile[CR]to login and continue"
msgstr "Agħżel il-profil tal-utent Kodi tiegħek[CR] biex tidħol u tkompli"

msgctxt "#31427"
msgid "Skin Shortcuts is responsible for handling all aspects of the main menu."
msgstr "Skin Shortcuts huwa responsabbli għall-immaniġġjar tal-aspetti kollha tal-menu prinċipali."

msgctxt "#31428"
msgid "The Grab Fanart script provides the random fanart slideshows for the main menu."
msgstr "L-iskrittura Grab Fanart tipprovdi l-wirjiet tal-fanart bl-addoċċ għall-menu prinċipali."

msgctxt "#31429"
msgid "Library Data Provider is a service that runs in the background to provide library data for widgets and live backgrounds as well as playlist statistics for infolines."
msgstr "Library Data Provider huwa servizz li jaħdem fl-isfond biex jipprovdi data tal-librerija għal widgets u sfondi ħajjin kif ukoll statistika tal-playlist għal infolines."

msgctxt "#31430"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white studio icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Addon tal-immaġni tar-riżorsi għall-wiri tal-ikoni tal-istudjo bojod default madwar il-ġilda."

msgctxt "#31431"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white recording label icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Addon ta 'l-immaġni tar-riżorsi għall-wiri ta' l-ikoni default tat-tikketta bojod tar-reġistrazzjoni madwar il-ġilda."

msgctxt "#31432"
msgid "Provides numerous Widget options and extended cast and crew metadata."
msgstr "Jipprovdi bosta għażliet ta’ Widget u metadejta estiża tal-cast u tal-ekwipaġġ."

msgctxt "#31433"
msgid "Skin Info Service is used to display movie set information throughout the skin."
msgstr "Skin Info Service jintuża biex juri l-informazzjoni tas-sett tal-films mal-ġilda kollha."

msgctxt "#31434"
msgid "Check MP3 Theme checks whether the user has put a theme.mp3 file in the corresponding movie/TV show folder to be played when browsing."
msgstr "Iċċekkja Theme MP3 jiċċekkja jekk l-utent poġġax fajl theme.mp3 fil-folder korrispondenti tal-film/televiżjoni biex jintlagħab waqt il-browsing."

msgctxt "#31450"
msgid "  •  Open Settings "
msgstr "• Iftaħ Settings"

msgctxt "#31451"
msgid "  •  Click to Install"
msgstr "• Ikklikkja biex Installa"

msgctxt "#31473"
msgid "Aeon Tajo Helper provides the data to display the cast for movies and TV shows."
msgstr "Aeon Tajo Helper jipprovdi d-dejta biex juri l-cast għal films u programmi tat-TV."

msgctxt "#31474"
msgid "CU LRC Lyrics is used to download, sync, and display lyrics during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "Il-Lirika CU LRC tintuża biex tniżżel, tissinkronizza u turi l-lirika waqt daqq tal-mużika fuq skrin sħiħ."

msgctxt "#31475"
msgid "Play Trailer makes possible to play movie trailers through a context menu. "
msgstr "Play Trailer jagħmilha possibbli li tilgħab karrijiet tal-films permezz ta' menu kuntestwali."

msgctxt "#31476"
msgid "Allows the use of Youtube to play trailers and other videos."
msgstr "Jippermetti l-użu ta 'Youtube biex tilgħab karrijiet u vidjows oħra."

msgctxt "#31477"
msgid "Provides some cast actress images to be shown in video views."
msgstr "Jipprovdi xi stampi ta' attriċi mitfugħa biex jintwerew f'veduti tal-vidjow."

msgctxt "#31478"
msgid "Artist Slideshow is used to display artist fanart for both the home screen and during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "Artist Slideshow jintuża biex juri l-fanart tal-artist kemm għall-iskrin tad-dar kif ukoll waqt daqq tal-mużika fuq skrin sħiħ."

msgctxt "#31479"
msgid "AutoCompletion provides suggestions to be selected while using the virtual keyboard."
msgstr "L-AutoCompletion jipprovdi suġġerimenti biex jintgħażlu waqt li tuża t-tastiera virtwali."

msgctxt "#31480"
msgid "Library Editor Script uses JSON to directly edit your database information."
msgstr "L-Iskript tal-Editur tal-Librerija juża JSON biex jeditja direttament l-informazzjoni tad-database tiegħek."

msgctxt "#31481"
msgid "Global Search makes possible to search among all the items (movies, TV shows, music, actors, etc.) in your collection."
msgstr "It-Tiftix Globali jagħmilha possibbli li tfittex fost l-oġġetti kollha (films, programmi televiżivi, mużika, atturi, eċċ.) fil-kollezzjoni tiegħek."

msgctxt "#31501"
msgid "Channel group"
msgstr "Grupp tal-kanali"

msgctxt "#31502"
msgid "Live TV"
msgstr "Live TV"

msgctxt "#31503"
msgid "Add Group"
msgstr "Żid Grupp"

msgctxt "#31504"
msgid "Rename Group"
msgstr "Semmi mill-ġdid tal-Grupp"

msgctxt "#31505"
msgid "Delete Group"
msgstr "Ħassar Grupp"

msgctxt "#31506"
msgid "Available[CR]Groups"
msgstr "Disponibbli[CR]Gruppi"

msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Channel Options"
msgstr "Għażliet tal-Kanal"

msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "Show similar movies in Shelf 3D view"
msgstr "Uri films simili fil-vista Shelf 3D"

msgctxt "#31901"
msgid "36 Hour Forecast"
msgstr "Tbassir ta' 36 Siegħa"

msgctxt "#31902"
msgid "Hourly Forecast"
msgstr "Tbassir fis-Siegħa"

msgctxt "#31903"
msgid "Weekend Forecast"
msgstr "Tbassir tal-Weekend"

msgctxt "#31904"
msgid "10 Day Forecast"
msgstr "Tbassir għal 10 Ijiem"

msgctxt "#31908"
msgid "Chance of Precipitation"
msgstr "Ċans ta' Preċipitazzjoni"

msgctxt "#31909"
msgid "Fetching forecast info..."
msgstr "Qed niġbru informazzjoni dwar it-tbassir..."

msgctxt "#31910"
msgid "Map & Alerts"
msgstr "Mappa u Twissijiet"

msgctxt "#31911"
msgid "Setup the Aeon Tajo main menu"
msgstr "Issettja l-menu prinċipali ta 'Aeon Tajo"

msgctxt "#31912"
msgid "Customize the main menu with widgets, backgrounds and statistics. Add your own custom main menu items."
msgstr "Ippersonalizza l-menu prinċipali b'widgets, sfondi u statistika.Żid l-oġġetti tal-menu prinċipali tad-dwana tiegħek."

msgctxt "#31913"
msgid "Aeon Tajo main menu vertical position"
msgstr "Aeon Tajo menu prinċipali pożizzjoni vertikali"

msgctxt "#31914"
msgid "Change the vertical position of the main menu. Default is centered on screen."
msgstr "Ibdel il-pożizzjoni vertikali tal-menu prinċipali.Default huwa ċċentrat fuq l-iskrin."

msgctxt "#31915"
msgid "Navigation style for horizontal lists"
msgstr "Stil ta' navigazzjoni għal listi orizzontali"

msgctxt "#31916"
msgid "Change the way horizontal lists scroll in Aeon Tajo. Default will scroll lists in a cycle. \"Fixed\" are lists with a beginning and end."
msgstr "Ibdel il-mod kif il-listi orizzontali jiskrolljaw f'Aeon Tajo.Default se tiskrollja l-listi f'ċiklu.\"Fissi\" huma listi b'bidu u tmiem."

msgctxt "#31917"
msgid "When enabled text scrolls automatically. When disabled manual scrolling is required. Note that most textboxes don't have a manual button."
msgstr "Meta ppermettiet it-test scrolls awtomatikament.Meta skrolljar manwali huwa meħtieġ.Innota li l-biċċa l-kbira tat-testboxes m'għandhomx buttuna manwali."

msgctxt "#31918"
msgid "Projects the current playing video on the background behind the panels."
msgstr "Jipproġetta l-video tal-logħob kurrenti fuq l-isfond wara l-pannelli."

msgctxt "#31919"
msgid "Projects the visualisation on the background behind the panels when music is played."
msgstr "Jipproġetta l-viżwalizzazzjoni fuq l-isfond wara l-pannelli meta tindaqq il-mużika."

msgctxt "#31920"
msgid "Displays a widget on the Home screen with media information when music is playing."
msgstr "Juri widget fuq l-iskrin Home b'informazzjoni tal-midja meta tkun qed tindaqq il-mużika."

msgctxt "#31921"
msgid "Displays a widget on the Home screen with media information when a movie or episode is playing."
msgstr "Juri widget fuq l-iskrin tad-dar b'informazzjoni tal-midja meta jkun qed jilgħab film jew episodju."

msgctxt "#31922"
msgid "This enables custom genre backgrounds when browsing through the videolibrary's genre node. Filenames should match the genre label. Extension must be .jpg."
msgstr "Dan jippermetti sfondi ta' ġeneri apposta meta tibbrawżja n-nodu tal-ġeneru tal-librerija tal-vidjo.L-ismijiet tal-fajls għandhom jaqblu mat-tikketta tal-ġeneru.L-estensjoni għandha tkun .jpg."

msgctxt "#31923"
msgid "Set a default select action to enable this item."
msgstr "Issettja azzjoni ta' għażla default biex din l-oġġett jiġi attivat."

msgctxt "#31924"
msgid "This enables custom genre backgrounds when browsing through the musiclibrary's genre node. Filenames should match the genre label. Extension must be .jpg."
msgstr "Dan jippermetti sfondi ta' ġeneru apposta meta tibbrawżja n-node tal-ġeneru tal-librerija mużikali.L-ismijiet tal-fajls għandhom jaqblu mat-tikketta tal-ġeneru.L-estensjoni għandha tkun .jpg."

msgctxt "#31925"
msgid "Pick one of the preset backgrounds or set your own images as the menu items background."
msgstr "Agħżel wieħed mill-isfond issettjati minn qabel jew issettja l-immaġini tiegħek bħala l-isfond tal-oġġetti tal-menu."

msgctxt "#31926"
msgid "Select add-ons, playlists or favourites. Choose 'Custom' for any of Kodi's built-in functions. (http://kodi.wiki/?title=List_of_Built_In_Functions)"
msgstr "Agħżel add-ons, playlists jew favoriti.Agħżel 'Custom' għal kwalunkwe funzjoni integrata ta' Kodi.(http://kodi.wiki/?title=List_of_Built_In_Functions)"

msgctxt "#31927"
msgid "Resets all above values to their defaults."
msgstr "Resets il-valuri kollha ta 'hawn fuq għall-inadempjenzi tagħhom."

msgctxt "#31928"
msgid "Aeon Tajo main menu layout"
msgstr "Tqassim tal-menu prinċipali Aeon Tajo"

msgctxt "#31929"
msgid "This setting defines how much items will be visible on the main menu. Options are 3 items or 5 items."
msgstr "Dan is-setting jiddefinixxi kemm oġġetti se jkunu viżibbli fil-menu prinċipali.L-għażliet huma 3 oġġetti jew 5 oġġetti."

msgctxt "#31930"
msgid "Choose a widget to display on the Home screen to have easy access to content from the library."
msgstr "Agħżel widget biex turi fuq l-iskrin tad-dar biex ikollok aċċess faċli għall-kontenut mil-librerija."

msgctxt "#31931"
msgid "Video plot preference"
msgstr "Preferenza tal-plott tal-vidjo"

msgctxt "#31932"
msgid "Show plot outline in the library views and full plot in the video information dialog or vice versa. Falls back to full plot if no outline is available."
msgstr "Uri l-kontorn tal-plott fil-veduti tal-librerija u l-plott sħiħ fid-djalogu tal-informazzjoni tal-vidjo jew viċi versa.Jaqa 'lura għall-plott sħiħ jekk l-ebda kontorn ma jkun disponibbli."

msgctxt "#31933"
msgid "Select an item to display on the left top of the main menu"
msgstr "Agħżel oġġett li turi fuq in-naħa ta' fuq tax-xellug tal-menu prinċipali"

msgctxt "#31935"
msgid "Switch places with another menu item. Opens a dialog with a list of menu items to choose from."
msgstr "Aqleb il-postijiet b'oġġett ieħor tal-menu.Tiftaħ djalogu b'lista ta' oġġetti tal-menu minn fejn tagħżel."

msgctxt "#31937"
msgid "Show the RSS feed on the bottom or top of the screen, depending on main menu position. Enabling this setting makes the submenu permanently visible."
msgstr "Uri l-RSS feed fuq il-qiegħ jew fuq tal-iskrin, skont il-pożizzjoni tal-menu prinċipali.L-attivazzjoni ta' dan is-setting tagħmel is-submenu viżibbli b'mod permanenti."

msgctxt "#31938"
msgid "Enables extra information in the TV show library, like TV show status, next / latest episode, etc. Depends on TV Show Next Aired add-on."
