msgctxt "#31290"
msgid "Thanks for using Aeon Tajo—I really hope you’re enjoying it. Creating and maintaining a Kodi skin like this takes hundreds of hours of work. If Aeon Tajo is something you enjoy and find useful, supporting it helps me keep working on it and ensures it can continue evolving in the future. [CR][CR]If you decide to do so, you’ll receive frequent updates with new features and bug fixes, along with videos, media packs, and easy-to-follow articles with detailed tips to help you get the most out of everything Aeon Tajo has to offer, together with my sincere gratitude for your support. [CR][CR]For more information, visit [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] and search for the creator [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], or go to [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Thanks!"
msgstr "Grazzi talli użajt Aeon Tajo—ni verament nittama li qed tgawdi.Il-ħolqien u ż-żamma ta 'ġilda Kodi bħal din tieħu mijiet ta' sigħat ta 'xogħol.Jekk Aeon Tajo hija xi ħaġa li tgawdi u ssibha utli, l-appoġġ tiegħu jgħinni nkompli naħdem fuqha u tiżgura li tkun tista' tkompli tevolvi fil-futur.[CR][CR]Jekk tiddeċiedi li tagħmel dan, tirċievi aġġornamenti frekwenti b'karatteristiċi ġodda u soluzzjoni ta' bugs, flimkien ma' vidjows, pakketti tal-midja, u artikli faċli biex isegwu b'suġġerimenti dettaljati biex jgħinuk tikseb l-aħjar minn dak kollu li Aeon Tajo għandha x'toffri, flimkien mal-gratitudni sinċiera tiegħi għall-appoġġ tiegħek.[CR][CR]Għal aktar informazzjoni, żur [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] u fittex il-kreatur [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], jew mur [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[k!][/COLOR]"

